  "name": "001 E Day 5 - Vision",
  "subject": "",
  "previewText": "",
  "html": "<!--\nSubject: {{contact.first_name}}, can you see it?\nPreview Text: Close your eyes. Picture your wedding day. Where are you standing?\n-->\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"und\" dir=\"auto\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\">\n  <head>\n    <title></title>\n    <!--[if !mso]><!-->\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <!--<![endif]-->\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n      #outlook a { padding:0; }\n      body { margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%; }\n      table, td { border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt; }\n      img { border:0;height:auto;line-height:100%; outline:none;text-decoration:none;-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic; }\n      p { display:block;margin:13px 0; }\n    </style>\n    <!--[if mso]>\n    <noscript>\n    <xml>\n    <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n      <o:AllowPNG/>\n      <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>\n    </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n    </xml>\n    </noscript>\n    <![endif]-->\n    <!--[if lte mso 11]>\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n      .mj-outlook-group-fix { width:100% !important; }\n    </style>\n    <![endif]-->\n    \n      <!--[if !mso]><!-->\n        <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n        <style type=\"text/css\">\n          @import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&display=swap);\n@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap);\n        </style>\n      <!--<![endif]-->\n\n    \n    \n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n      @media only screen and (min-width:480px) {\n        .mj-column-per-100 { width:100% !important; max-width: 100%; }\n      }\n    </style>\n    <style media=\"screen and (min-width:480px)\">\n      .moz-text-html .mj-column-per-100 { width:100% !important; max-width: 100%; }\n    </style>\n    \n    \n  \n    \n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n\n    @media only screen and (max-width:479px) {\n      table.mj-full-width-mobile { width: 100% !important; }\n      td.mj-full-width-mobile { width: auto !important; }\n    }\n  \n    </style>\n     \n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n/* Progressive enhancement for email clients with CSS support */\n      .heading-primary {\n        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif !important;\n        color: #2C3E50 !important;\n        font-weight: 500 !important;\n        font-size: 32px !important;\n        line-height: 1.2 !important;\n      }\n      .heading-secondary {\n        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif !important;\n        color: #2C3E50 !important;\n        font-weight: 500 !important;\n        font-size: 24px !important;\n        line-height: 1.3 !important;\n      }\n      .body-text {\n        font-family: 'Poppins', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n        color: #4A4A4A !important;\n        font-size: 16px !important;\n        line-height: 1.6 !important;\n      }\n      .signature-text {\n        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif !important;\n        color: #2C3E50 !important;\n        font-size: 20px !important;\n        font-weight: 500 !important;\n      }\n      .testimonial-quote {\n        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif !important;\n        color: #2C3E50 !important;\n        font-size: 20px !important;\n        font-style: italic !important;\n        line-height: 1.4 !important;\n      }\n      .testimonial-attribution {\n        font-family: 'Poppins', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n        color: #666 !important;\n        font-size: 14px !important;\n        font-weight: 500 !important;\n      }\n      .quote-text {\n        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif !important;\n        color: #2C3E50 !important;\n        font-size: 22px !important;\n        font-style: italic !important;\n        line-height: 1.4 !important;\n      }\n      /* Mobile optimizations */\n      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {\n        .heading-primary { font-size: 26px !important; }\n        .heading-secondary { font-size: 21px !important; }\n        .body-text div { font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 1.6 !important; }\n        .testimonial-quote div { font-size: 18px !important; }\n        .quote-text div { font-size: 20px !important; }\n        /* Full-width mobile buttons */\n        .cta-primary table,\n        .cta-secondary table { width: 100% !important; }\n        .cta-primary a,\n        .cta-secondary a { display: block !important; width: 100% !important; }\n        .footer-email a { font-size: 11px !important; }\n        .responsive-link a { font-size: 12px !important; word-break: break-all; }\n      }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (headings) and Poppins (body) -->\n<!-- Global Attributes -->\n<!-- Custom Styles -->\n<!-- Preview Text -->\n  <!-- outlook-fixes-applied --></head>\n  <body style=\"word-spacing:normal;background-color:#FAFAFA;\">\n    \n    <div style=\"display:none;font-size:1px;color:#ffffff;line-height:1px;max-height:0px;max-width:0px;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;\">Close your eyes. Picture your wedding day. Where are you standing?</div>\n  \n    \n      <div\n         aria-roledescription=\"email\" style=\"background-color:#FAFAFA;\" role=\"article\" lang=\"und\" dir=\"auto\"\n      >\n        <!-- Opening Content (above the fold) --><!-- Gallery Section (between opening and body) --><!-- Body Content -->\n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#FDFCFA\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#FDFCFA;background-color:#FDFCFA;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#FDFCFA;background-color:#FDFCFA;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:40px 40px 20px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 25px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond, Georgia, serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.6;text-align:left;color:#2C3E50;\"\n      >{{contact.first_name}},</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 15px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      >Here's a question worth sitting with for a minute \u2014 maybe with your coffee this morning, or as you're winding down this evening:</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:25px 0;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond, Georgia, serif;font-size:24px;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;color:#D4AF37;\"\n      >When you picture your wedding day \u2014 really picture it, in vivid detail \u2014 where are you?</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n          <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n    \n    <!-- Vision 1: Ceremony -->\n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:30px 40px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 20px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      ><strong>Can you see yourself</strong> walking down an aisle surrounded by ancient trees, with golden sunlight filtering through the branches, your closest people seated on either side as you make your way toward the person you love?</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            <!-- IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: Garden Ceremony --><!--\n          <mj-image\n            src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/G7APqyfJ6lyi4l28noZj/media/6989327a0a7fd1cf9141c545.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Garden Ceremony\"\n            width=\"520px\"\n            border-radius=\"6px\"\n            padding=\"0\" />\n          -->\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n          <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n    \n    <!-- Vision 2: Cocktail Hour -->\n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#F5F1EB\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#F5F1EB;background-color:#F5F1EB;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#F5F1EB;background-color:#F5F1EB;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:30px 40px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 20px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      ><strong>Can you hear</strong> the sound of your guests' laughter floating across the lawn during cocktail hour, the clink of glasses as people toast to your future, the murmur of conversation as everyone enjoys being together?</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            <!-- IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: Cocktail hour on the lawn --><!--\n          <mj-image\n            src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/G7APqyfJ6lyi4l28noZj/media/6989327a0708e4880ea07007.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Cocktail hour on the lawn\"\n            width=\"520px\"\n            border-radius=\"6px\"\n            padding=\"0\" />\n          -->\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n          <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n    \n    <!-- Vision 3: Reception -->\n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:30px 40px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 20px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      ><strong>Can you feel</strong> what it's like to step into your reception space, look around, and see everyone you love in one room \u2014 your families, your friends, the people who've shaped who you are as a couple \u2014 all gathered here to celebrate you?</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            <!-- IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: Reception details --><!--\n          <mj-image\n            src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/G7APqyfJ6lyi4l28noZj/media/6989327a0708e4880ea07007.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Reception details\"\n            width=\"520px\"\n            border-radius=\"6px\"\n            padding=\"0\" />\n          -->\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n          <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#2C3E50\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#2C3E50;background-color:#2C3E50;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#2C3E50;background-color:#2C3E50;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:40px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 15px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond, Georgia, serif;font-size:22px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;color:#D4AF37;\"\n      >\"That feeling \u2014 that moment of clarity when you can actually see your memories happening \u2014 that's what matters.\"</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"center\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:10px 0 0;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:center;color:#E8E8E8;\"\n      >The venue you choose should be the place where you can genuinely see your memories happening. Where you can imagine your dad's toast, your first dance, the moment you look around the room and think, 'We did this. This is ours.'</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n          <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n      \n      <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:600px;\" width=\"600\" bgcolor=\"#FDFCFA\" ><tr><td style=\"line-height:0px;font-size:0px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><![endif]-->\n    \n      \n      <div  style=\"background:#FDFCFA;background-color:#FDFCFA;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;\">\n        \n        <table\n           align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:#FDFCFA;background-color:#FDFCFA;width:100%;\"\n        >\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td\n                 style=\"direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:40px 40px 20px;text-align:center;\"\n              >\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:520px;\" ><![endif]-->\n            \n      <div\n         class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\" style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\"\n      >\n        \n      <table\n         border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\"\n      >\n        <tbody>\n          \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 15px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond, Georgia, serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.6;text-align:left;color:#2C3E50;\"\n      >Is That Cameron Estate for You?</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 15px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      >I don't know the answer to that question yet. But I'd love to give you the chance to find out.</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 15px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      >I've watched hundreds of couples tour Cameron Estate over the years, and here's what I've noticed: the ones who book with us \u2014 the couples who decide \"yes, this is it\" \u2014 they usually get quiet for a second during the tour. They're not looking at the chandeliers anymore.</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            \n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-size:0px;padding:0 0 25px;word-break:break-word;\"\n                >\n                  \n      <div\n         style=\"font-family:Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;color:#4A4A4A;\"\n      >They're looking at each other. And you can see it click. They're not seeing <em>a</em> wedding anymore. They're seeing <em>their</em> wedding.</div>\n    \n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            <!--\n          <mj-button \n            href=\"{{ links.book_tour }}\" \n            background-color=\"#D4AF37\" \n            color=\"#FFFFFF\"\n            border-radius=\"4px\"\n            font-size=\"16px\"\n            font-weight=\"500\"\n            inner-padding=\"14px 35px\"\n            align=\"left\"\n            padding-bottom=\"25px\">\n            Schedule Your Private Tour\n          </mj-button>\n          -->\n              <tr>\n                <td\n                   align=\"left\" class=\"